This is caused by an incompatibility between the Android Studio and Redis versions You can reach me at johndoe@email.com.. Despite attempts to restart the dashboard and review Redis logs, the issue remains unresolved. I would appreciate your help in addressing this problem and taking steps to avoid future disruptions. My name is Omar Hassan.
